                    <img class="article-category-section-img" src="//a.c-dn.net/c/content/igcom/zh_CN/ig-financial-markets/market-news-and-analysis/highlights/2017/11/16/aramco-ipo-_-london-or-new-york-40707/jcr:content/textimage/image.img.jpg/1510814904597.jpg" alt="IG Spread betting and CFD Trading">
                

                <div class="article-category-section-synopsis">伦敦和纽约正在为成为沙特阿美石油公司的IPO地点进行激烈争夺，而最终赢家将会赚得盆满钵盈。</div>
                
                    
                        
                        
                            
                                
                                
                                    <span class="article-category-section-author"><a class="secondary" href="/zh/profile/ig-simplified"><strong>IG集团</strong></a>,</span>
                                
                            
                        
                    
                
                
                    <span class="article-category-section-date time" data-datetime="2017-11-16T07:09:22+0000">2017-11-16T07:09:22+0000</span>
                
            </div>
        </div>
    </li>

        
        
    

